      "author": "nauppece",
      "description": "TimeMeter 0.1.0 — first public release.\n\nAuto-tracks the frontmost macOS app to Markdown, with a sidebar (today/day/month), timeline zoom, per-app show/exclude, quick notes, daily-report draft, and click-a-bar-to-append-to-a-note. Desktop tracking uses osascript/ioreg; mobile is view/manual-log only.\n\nManual install: put main.js, manifest.json, styles.css into <vault>/.obsidian/plugins/timemeter/ and enable in Community plugins.",
